Creates an empty `BinaryHeap` as a max-heap, using `A` as allocator.

# Examples

Basic usage:

```
#![feature(allocator_api)]

use std::alloc::System;
use std::collections::BinaryHeap;
let mut heap = BinaryHeap::new_in(System);
heap.push(4);
```
